revision.text: ==English== ===Proper noun=== {{en-proper noun|Yetters}} # {{surname|en}}. ===Statistics=== * According to the 2010 United States Census, ''Yetter'' is the 10959<sup>th</sup> most common surname in the United States, belonging to 2903 individuals. ''Yetter'' is most common among White (95.14%) individuals.
